5 wonderful years! It's been truly a blessing! I'm thankful God allowed me to have this opportunity. It's not something I ever planned for or dreamed of, it's more than I could have dreamed of. 🧡

I am walking away because God has laid it on my heart to take a step back and soak in the time I have with my family. It took me two years to take this step, but I'm doing it and I'm excited to see how God uses this opportunity and time!

Thank you for being here and being so wonderful to me! There are no words to tell you how full my heart is. I just feel beyond grateful to have had this page, community and friends!

I'm keeping the page up and I plan to do bimonthly updates so stay tuned!!!!

🧡🧡🧡

Hi friends!!!!
It’s a new year so I thought I would reintroduce myself and answer some questions!!!

My name is Caroline and I’m a wife (we just celebrated #18) and a mom of four kids 17, 15, 13 & 12! And a dog mom, cat mom and turtle mom 😂😂

We live in Kansas and we love our little community of friends here, we have been blessed to find lifelong friends that we are raising our kids and doing life with!!

I love Jesus!! My faith is apart of me in every aspect! 

I just started a new job and it’s been an adjustment but I couldn’t have asked for a better company to work for! This is actually my work picture!! Photo credit Anna!!!

I am a cheer, dance, baseball and soccer mom, aka taxi driver! I love being with these kids even if it’s in a car driving! I am not looking forward to my oldest being a senior next year 😭

My favorite thing to do is play games or watch movies with my family!! Favorite movie: The Proposal!!
Favorite game: Clue (I always win!!)

I started this account to share DIY’s and decor. Last year I took a step back to refocus and prioritize my time. Now I am back and I’ll be here to share once and awhile. It won’t be an everyday thing any more. 

I am glad you are here and especially if you have been here since I started CB Designs in 2018! Thank you!! 🧡🧡

I can’t wait to see what 2024 brings!!! If anything I hope it brings you and me an abundance of joy! 😘😘

The high this weekend is 6° here!!! 😱 I have no plans to go anywhere except my sofa with junie 😂🤣

Stay warm friends!!
